1
00:00:06,000 --> 00:00:08,702
♫  I want to go to the future  ♫

2
00:00:08,702 --> 00:00:12,157
♫  Time has bear witness to my quirkiness  ♫

3
00:00:12,157 --> 00:00:18,250
♫  I want to seize the day and put the whole world into my head  ♫

4
00:00:18,250 --> 00:00:24,476
♫  I want to go back in time to do all the crazy things I didn't do  ♫

5
00:00:24,476 --> 00:00:30,997
♫  Don't say goodbye, don't be in a daze, let my radiant light be bright  ♫

6
00:00:30,997 --> 00:00:35,983
♫  We are always looking forward to the unknown future  ♫

7
00:00:35,983 --> 00:00:43,283
♫  And often overlooking our surroundings and best plan in front of us  ♫

8
00:00:43,283 --> 00:00:48,307
♫  Every day my heart beats for you  ♫

9
00:00:48,307 --> 00:00:49,820
♫  Be your light  ♫

10
00:00:49,820 --> 00:00:55,683
♫  You are no doubt irreplaceable  ♫

11
00:00:55,683 --> 00:01:01,983
♫  Every day the sun shines through the window  ♫

12
00:01:01,983 --> 00:01:08,150
♫  With the reflection of you being my incredible highlight  ♫

13
00:01:08,150 --> 00:01:11,757
[I Don't Want to be Brothers with You]

14
00:01:12,599 --> 00:01:15,100
Gao Yang, the more I look at you, the happier I get.

15
00:01:15,100 --> 00:01:18,090
Tell me what you want to eat. I'll go make them for you.

16
00:01:18,090 --> 00:01:23,210
I'll take Xiaowen home soon. He's been staying at your place for a week.

17
00:01:23,210 --> 00:01:25,779
Some snacks will do.

18
00:01:26,419 --> 00:01:28,139
Sure.

19
00:01:29,699 --> 00:01:32,100
Who said I was going home with you?

20
00:01:33,319 --> 00:01:34,779
We'll get the results back soon.

21
00:01:34,779 --> 00:01:37,160
Well, let's talk after we get the results.

22
00:01:37,160 --> 00:01:40,599
Why are you so stubborn? What's a few more days?

23
00:01:41,050 --> 00:01:43,030
Xiaowen,

24
00:01:43,799 --> 00:01:47,259
Mr. Gao is really a good person. We can't treat him like this.

25
00:01:47,300 --> 00:01:51,600
Without Mr. Gao, we wouldn't be where we are today.

26
00:01:52,600 --> 00:01:59,150
Exactly, Xiaowen. Look, Mr. Gao didn't ask for anything.

27
00:01:59,150 --> 00:02:02,740
He... he helped me selflessly too, right?

28
00:02:02,740 --> 00:02:08,240
Exactly. Just get over it. Come on, eat some jujube.

29
00:02:08,240 --> 00:02:10,006
Come on.

30
00:02:11,190 --> 00:02:12,831
You and your stubbornness.

31
00:02:12,831 --> 00:02:16,580
[Episode 7: We Had a Deal]

32
00:02:16,580 --> 00:02:18,240
Look at this.

33
00:02:18,240 --> 00:02:22,920
Look at this. Why are you so stubborn?

34
00:02:22,920 --> 00:02:27,439
Wenjing and I haven't even held hands. How could you be my son?

35
00:02:28,810 --> 00:02:31,599
Youngsters are so impulsive these days.

36
00:02:31,599 --> 00:02:34,520
Why must you waste money on that?

37
00:02:38,119 --> 00:02:40,119
No, no.

38
00:02:41,539 --> 00:02:45,700
He's not Gao Yang. I can't scold him like that.

39
00:02:49,199 --> 00:02:52,179
Xiaowen, let's go home.

40
00:02:52,179 --> 00:02:55,960
I'll make you pork knuckle if you come home. Does that sound good?

41
00:03:02,090 --> 00:03:04,560
Xiaowen, about the results...

42
00:03:06,180 --> 00:03:07,919
What's going on here?

43
00:03:07,919 --> 00:03:09,420
He's still angry.

44
00:03:09,420 --> 00:03:10,740
What did you say?

45
00:03:10,740 --> 00:03:15,199
What can I say? I just put in a good word for you. Take this.

46
00:03:18,599 --> 00:03:20,979
What an unfilial son.

47
00:03:22,219 --> 00:03:26,279
Here, let me wind it up for you. Here we go.

48
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:29,819
Ye Jun. Come take a picture of me and the baby.

49
00:03:29,819 --> 00:03:31,504
Sure.

50
00:03:39,740 --> 00:03:41,960
Why didn't Anna come?

51
00:03:41,960 --> 00:03:45,960
She... She's a very jealous woman. I didn't tell her I was coming here.

52
00:03:45,960 --> 00:03:48,064
I don't want to give her the wrong idea.

53
00:03:49,140 --> 00:03:51,419
I don't even mind. Why does she care?

54
00:03:51,419 --> 00:03:52,700
It happened a long time ago.

55
00:03:52,700 --> 00:03:55,360
Not just because of Wenjing, she's also upset about something else.

56
00:03:55,360 --> 00:03:57,140
You have more old flames?

57
00:03:57,140 --> 00:03:59,199
That's not true. Come on, take a picture.

58
00:03:59,199 --> 00:04:01,840
Xiaowen, over here. Look at the camera.

59
00:04:01,840 --> 00:04:04,460
Three, two, one,

60
00:04:04,460 --> 00:04:06,879
cheese!

61
00:04:12,700 --> 00:04:15,800
[No. 3 Tian Yuan High School]

62
00:04:16,470 --> 00:04:19,924
- Xiaowen.
- Xiao... Xiaowen!

63
00:04:23,620 --> 00:04:25,720
- Go check on him.
- Why don't you go?

64
00:04:25,720 --> 00:04:28,000
You're his buddy.

65
00:04:28,000 --> 00:04:32,134
What if Xiaowen takes things too hard and runs away again?

66
00:04:38,859 --> 00:04:43,920
- Xiaowen.
- Mr. Gao, how does this game console work?

67
00:04:47,979 --> 00:04:52,860
Let me tell you, B is to shoot. A is to jump. Just follow me. It's starting.

68
00:04:52,860 --> 00:04:55,720
Gao Yang, it's Xiaowen's first time. Cut him some slack.

69
00:04:55,720 --> 00:04:57,539
We're on the same team.

70
00:04:57,539 --> 00:04:59,060
Well, protect him then.

71
00:04:59,060 --> 00:05:02,059
Don't worry. I'm really good.

72
00:05:04,500 --> 00:05:07,450
I told you to be quiet. I was distracted.

73
00:05:07,450 --> 00:05:12,339
Noob. Come on. My turn!

74
00:05:14,120 --> 00:05:15,704
- Out of my way.
- No, no.

75
00:05:15,704 --> 00:05:16,729
- Go away.
- No.

76
00:05:16,729 --> 00:05:18,100
- Give it to me.
- You never played before.

77
00:05:18,100 --> 00:05:20,320
- Out of my way.
- Hurry up.

78
00:05:20,759 --> 00:05:23,620
- B is to shoot and A is to jump, okay?
- B is to shoot.

79
00:05:23,620 --> 00:05:25,649
A is to jump.

80
00:05:32,219 --> 00:05:33,836
Xiaowen,

81
00:05:35,419 --> 00:05:37,020
I did have a crush on your mom.

82
00:05:37,020 --> 00:05:38,539
- What?
- I shouldn't keep it from you.

83
00:05:38,539 --> 00:05:42,020
But it was a purely platonic friendship between your mom and me. We never even held hands.

84
00:05:42,020 --> 00:05:44,959
I just thought it was really embarrassing. That's why I didn't tell you.

85
00:05:44,959 --> 00:05:46,419
Besides,

86
00:05:46,419 --> 00:05:49,919
that happened so many years ago.

87
00:05:49,919 --> 00:05:53,880
- Xiaowen... I...
- Dodge the bullets.

88
00:05:55,319 --> 00:05:57,060
Be gentle! Don't break it.

89
00:05:57,060 --> 00:05:59,079
It's only 99 yuan. I'll buy another one if I break it.

90
00:05:59,079 --> 00:06:03,079
Yeah, right. You spent a month's salary on that DNA test, right?

91
00:06:05,560 --> 00:06:07,580
It's... it's worth it.

92
00:06:07,580 --> 00:06:09,224
Exactly!

93
00:06:17,140 --> 00:06:18,902
Xiaowen,

94
00:06:18,902 --> 00:06:22,500
just stay here, okay?

95
00:06:24,399 --> 00:06:25,820
Say something, will you?

96
00:06:25,820 --> 00:06:28,420
Xiaowen, say something.

97
00:06:28,420 --> 00:06:31,179
Mr. Gao, I'm sorry.

98
00:06:39,140 --> 00:06:43,299
Why are you apologizing? Well, you can't run away again in the future.

99
00:06:43,299 --> 00:06:46,058
That's right. Don't run away again.

100
00:06:53,579 --> 00:06:55,879
- Come on, have a banana.
- Come on, have a banana.

101
00:06:55,879 --> 00:06:59,639
Here, here. Xiaowen, don't go hungry.

102
00:06:59,639 --> 00:07:02,139
- What about mine?
- Here, here.

103
00:07:02,139 --> 00:07:06,460
- Let's keep playing.
- All right, continue. Let's continue. Here, here.

104
00:07:12,360 --> 00:07:13,480
Dad.

105
00:07:13,480 --> 00:07:16,119
Daddy, I can't hold it anymore.

106
00:07:16,119 --> 00:07:17,999
You can't hold it anymore?

107
00:07:18,600 --> 00:07:21,639
Why were you so energetic when you were gossiping?

108
00:07:21,639 --> 00:07:24,120
Mr. Gao and I were on such good terms.

109
00:07:24,120 --> 00:07:27,679
You almost ruined it. How am I supposed to face him now?

110
00:07:27,679 --> 00:07:29,380
What are you doing?

111
00:07:31,199 --> 00:07:33,979
You and mom said it.

112
00:07:33,979 --> 00:07:36,859
Did I say the words "illegitimate son"?

113
00:07:36,859 --> 00:07:40,179
Just because Gao Bin had a crush on Wenjing, Ye Xiaowen has to be their child?

114
00:07:40,179 --> 00:07:43,020
Why are you imaginative?

115
00:07:43,020 --> 00:07:45,360
Why? You have nothing to say now?

116
00:07:45,360 --> 00:07:46,620
You told me to be quiet.

117
00:07:46,620 --> 00:07:48,576
Well, be quiet then!

118
00:07:49,660 --> 00:07:51,399
Look, it's 10 o'clock now.

119
00:07:51,399 --> 00:07:56,700
Dou Dou, let your sister come down when it's 10:30.

120
00:07:57,700 --> 00:08:01,059
I... Dad!

121
00:08:04,560 --> 00:08:08,020
Sister, what are you doing? Dad told me to keep an eye on you.

122
00:08:08,020 --> 00:08:10,480
Are you asking for a beating, you little bastard?

123
00:08:10,480 --> 00:08:14,900
You promised to love me for the rest of my life.

124
00:08:18,290 --> 00:08:22,039
Fine. Dou Dou Honey, please let me rest for a while.

125
00:08:22,039 --> 00:08:24,560
No, but I can help you.

126
00:08:24,560 --> 00:08:26,430
That's more like it.

127
00:08:30,460 --> 00:08:32,355
What are you doing?

128
00:08:35,500 --> 00:08:37,500
Dad! Look at him!

129
00:08:37,500 --> 00:08:39,840
Hold it up! Don't move!

130
00:08:43,579 --> 00:08:45,700
- The phone is ringing!
- Give it to me.

131
00:08:45,700 --> 00:08:48,668
Go answer the phone. Hurry up! I'm playing here!

132
00:08:51,380 --> 00:08:54,620
If it's Old Jin, tell him I'm not here.

133
00:08:55,159 --> 00:08:57,240
Hello, Gao Bin isn't here.

134
00:09:01,600 --> 00:09:03,432
Who is it?

135
00:09:08,299 --> 00:09:10,319
My mom.

136
00:09:10,319 --> 00:09:12,759
What is she up to now?

137
00:09:12,759 --> 00:09:16,394
She said she's coming over next month and taking me to Beijing for school!

138
00:09:23,399 --> 00:09:26,860
We'll go to Tiananmen to watch the flag-raising ceremony.

139
00:09:26,860 --> 00:09:30,460
After that, we'll eat at Quanjude.

140
00:09:30,460 --> 00:09:32,159
At noon, we'll go watch a movie.

141
00:09:32,159 --> 00:09:35,640
At night, we'll go to the Worker's Stadium.

142
00:09:35,640 --> 00:09:37,807
You're really going to Beijing?

143
00:09:44,480 --> 00:09:46,619
Why are you sighing?

144
00:09:46,619 --> 00:09:47,980
I'm so worried.

145
00:09:47,980 --> 00:09:49,712
Worried about what?

146
00:09:50,459 --> 00:09:54,479
Gao Bin. He won't let me go for sure.

147
00:09:55,939 --> 00:09:58,239
Have a nice chat with him.

148
00:09:58,239 --> 00:10:02,600
Chat about what? If he's willing to listen, I would be there already.

149
00:10:04,939 --> 00:10:08,040
Forget him. I want to go to Beijing.

150
00:10:09,039 --> 00:10:12,060
Xiaowen, after I leave,

151
00:10:12,060 --> 00:10:14,579
will you be alright with Gao Bin by yourself?

152
00:10:14,579 --> 00:10:18,059
None of your business. We'll be fine.

153
00:10:22,919 --> 00:10:26,559
Xiaowen, let me ask you something.

154
00:10:29,960 --> 00:10:31,720
Have you been to Beijing?

155
00:10:32,440 --> 00:10:33,879
No.

156
00:10:36,559 --> 00:10:38,336
Do you think...

157
00:10:38,336 --> 00:10:42,700
there will be girls as pretty as Mi Jia in Beijing?

158
00:10:42,700 --> 00:10:44,419
- Yes.
- Really?

159
00:10:44,419 --> 00:10:46,499
They will be prettier.

160
00:10:46,499 --> 00:10:48,320
Go see them now.

161
00:10:48,320 --> 00:10:50,980
- Won't you miss me?
- I...

162
00:10:53,799 --> 00:10:55,538
Mr. Gao,

163
00:11:11,100 --> 00:11:12,923
what are you doing?

164
00:11:23,240 --> 00:11:25,160
There's a mosquito.

165
00:11:25,879 --> 00:11:28,220
Is this the mosquito season?

166
00:11:28,220 --> 00:11:29,659
You don't know?

167
00:11:29,659 --> 00:11:32,720
Spring mosquitoes are as fierce as tigers.

168
00:11:32,720 --> 00:11:34,140
I just found one.

169
00:11:34,140 --> 00:11:37,700
It looks dignified and strong.

170
00:11:37,700 --> 00:11:39,754
Were you eavesdropping?

171
00:11:40,559 --> 00:11:42,360
Yang Yang, come here.

172
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:44,740
Take a seat. Let's talk.

173
00:11:52,820 --> 00:11:54,752
Yang Yang.

174
00:11:58,000 --> 00:12:01,316
Brother Yang, are you getting hungry?

175
00:12:01,316 --> 00:12:02,740
Have a banana.

176
00:12:02,740 --> 00:12:05,459
I don't want it. I'll eat it in Beijing.

177
00:12:13,339 --> 00:12:15,779
Well, here's what I think.

178
00:12:15,779 --> 00:12:23,020
I don't care if you want to go to Beijing, Shanghai, New York, London, or even Mars.

179
00:12:23,020 --> 00:12:24,860
That's fine.

180
00:12:24,860 --> 00:12:28,600
However, you're at a very critical intersection in your life.

181
00:12:28,600 --> 00:12:32,420
in your life.

182
00:12:32,420 --> 00:12:34,440
If you make one wrong step,

183
00:12:34,440 --> 00:12:37,879
you might regret it for the rest of your life.

184
00:12:37,879 --> 00:12:42,319
Based on your logic, aren't schools in Beijing even better?

185
00:12:42,319 --> 00:12:45,739
Are you an idiot?

186
00:12:45,739 --> 00:12:48,080
Think about what you have at No. 3 High School of Tieyuan.

187
00:12:48,080 --> 00:12:50,659
There's me, Principal Jin, Wu Dibao,

188
00:12:50,659 --> 00:12:54,639
Jin Beibei, and all your classmates to tutor you, supervise you, and help you.

189
00:12:54,639 --> 00:12:59,200
What kind of privilege is that? Normal people would never have that kind of privilege. Do you know that?

190
00:12:59,220 --> 00:13:01,620
Do you know how I'm treated in No. 3 High School?

191
00:13:01,620 --> 00:13:04,500
Everyone revolves around you.

192
00:13:06,579 --> 00:13:11,259
Just stay right here in Tieyuan. Listen to me.

193
00:13:11,259 --> 00:13:12,579
Brother Bin, I understand.

194
00:13:12,579 --> 00:13:13,960
Do you understand?

195
00:13:13,960 --> 00:13:15,779
I've decided to go to Beijing.

196
00:13:15,779 --> 00:13:17,200
I refuse!

197
00:13:17,200 --> 00:13:18,940
Your words don't count.

198
00:13:18,940 --> 00:13:20,414
I...

199
00:13:24,300 --> 00:13:28,759
Yang Yang, you're such an unfaithful friend.

200
00:13:29,840 --> 00:13:31,779
We just told Xiaowen

201
00:13:31,779 --> 00:13:35,819
to stay here with us and not go anywhere.

202
00:13:35,819 --> 00:13:37,559
If you leave, who will take care of him?

203
00:13:37,559 --> 00:13:39,059
Xiaowen said don't mind him.

204
00:13:39,059 --> 00:13:43,160
What about Mi Jia? If you go to Beijing, you won't be able to see Mi Jia!

205
00:13:43,160 --> 00:13:44,980
And you said you weren't eavesdropping.

206
00:13:44,980 --> 00:13:48,009
Beijing has Wang Cailing.

207
00:13:48,009 --> 00:13:50,148
Go to bed now.

208
00:14:02,130 --> 00:14:04,050
[Wisdom, Enthusiasm, and Diligence]

209
00:14:04,050 --> 00:14:05,698
Hurry.

210
00:14:08,120 --> 00:14:10,048
Comfort her.

211
00:14:14,339 --> 00:14:15,900
Beibei, Beibei.

212
00:14:15,900 --> 00:14:18,159
It's not that bad. Just get over it.

213
00:14:18,159 --> 00:14:21,500
I'm just going to Beijing. It's not like we'll never see each other again.

214
00:14:21,500 --> 00:14:26,559
Well, are you coming home during breaks?

215
00:14:26,559 --> 00:14:29,659
Of course. I'll bring you a roast duck.

216
00:14:29,659 --> 00:14:33,540
Can't you just stay?

217
00:14:33,540 --> 00:14:35,620
I can't do that, Beibei.

218
00:14:35,620 --> 00:14:38,159
I'm a man, a lone wolf in the wind.

219
00:14:38,159 --> 00:14:39,659
I have set out on an adventure.

220
00:14:39,659 --> 00:14:43,020
Here you go again!

221
00:14:43,020 --> 00:14:45,019
Meng.

222
00:14:46,879 --> 00:14:50,720
Gao Yang, what school will you go to in Beijing?

223
00:14:50,720 --> 00:14:53,859
My mom would certainly find me a nice school.

224
00:14:53,859 --> 00:14:56,740
Well, you should study hard when you go to a nice school.

225
00:14:56,740 --> 00:14:59,159
There will be a lot of good students. Don't make a fool of yourself.

226
00:14:59,159 --> 00:15:00,980
I won't.

227
00:15:02,419 --> 00:15:04,719
This is for you.

228
00:15:04,719 --> 00:15:08,041
- It's really expensive. Don't break it.
- Hurry up.

229
00:15:08,980 --> 00:15:11,500
Don't Leave If You Love Me.

230
00:15:11,500 --> 00:15:13,241
Jiabao...

231
00:15:16,100 --> 00:15:17,799
If I'm not leaving,

232
00:15:17,799 --> 00:15:23,219
I really wouldn't know how important I am to you guys.

233
00:15:24,900 --> 00:15:27,040
All right, all right.

234
00:15:27,800 --> 00:15:32,299
Beibei, stop crying. Don't you still have me after Gao Yang leaves?

235
00:15:35,080 --> 00:15:36,879
Stop crying.

236
00:15:36,879 --> 00:15:38,140
Stop talking.

237
00:15:38,140 --> 00:15:41,499
Beibei. Beibei, Beibei,

238
00:15:41,499 --> 00:15:42,779
how about this?

239
00:15:42,779 --> 00:15:44,485
You should give me a present too.

240
00:15:45,339 --> 00:15:48,680
You're awful!

241
00:15:48,680 --> 00:15:51,200
Stop irritating her.

242
00:15:51,200 --> 00:15:53,480
All right, don't cry.

243
00:15:53,480 --> 00:15:54,960
All right.

244
00:15:54,960 --> 00:15:57,128
- All right.
- Just get over it.

245
00:16:01,639 --> 00:16:03,200
Look at how nice they are to me.

246
00:16:03,200 --> 00:16:05,399
Shouldn't you do something for me too?

247
00:16:05,399 --> 00:16:07,359
Must you go to Beijing?

248
00:16:07,399 --> 00:16:09,940
I have to, right?

249
00:16:09,940 --> 00:16:13,760
When I move to Beijing, I can get away from Gao Bin.

250
00:16:13,760 --> 00:16:17,560
Although we're doing better after you arrived,

251
00:16:17,560 --> 00:16:19,399
I have no choice.

252
00:16:19,399 --> 00:16:20,860
My mom and I had a deal.

253
00:16:20,860 --> 00:16:24,060
She'll take me away when I grow up.

254
00:16:24,060 --> 00:16:27,759
Sorry, Bro, I can't watch over you anymore.

255
00:16:29,559 --> 00:16:31,121
This is for you.

256
00:16:31,939 --> 00:16:33,659
What is it?

257
00:16:34,480 --> 00:16:38,020
Study notes from this semester. Take it with you and look through it.

258
00:16:38,020 --> 00:16:40,780
Why are you giving this to me? Can I understand it?

259
00:16:40,780 --> 00:16:43,930
- Give it back then.
- No.

260
00:16:43,930 --> 00:16:46,859
It's your good intention after all. It's the thought that counts.

261
00:16:46,859 --> 00:16:48,579
I was the one who raised Gao Yang.
[Principal's Office]

262
00:16:48,579 --> 00:16:50,720
What did you do for him since he was 6 years old?

263
00:16:50,720 --> 00:16:52,419
Now you want to take my son away?

264
00:16:52,419 --> 00:16:54,779
Who would do something like that?

265
00:16:55,260 --> 00:16:56,440
Calm down.

266
00:16:56,440 --> 00:16:59,160
I am really calm!

267
00:16:59,160 --> 00:17:01,239
I don't want to talk to you!

268
00:17:01,960 --> 00:17:03,800
What? No, don't.

269
00:17:03,800 --> 00:17:06,600
What meeting again? You... I...

270
00:17:06,600 --> 00:17:08,820
What the hell!

271
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:14,480
Old Jin, tell me, why would there be a mother like her?

272
00:17:14,480 --> 00:17:17,000
I'm not his mom. How would I know?

273
00:17:17,000 --> 00:17:18,832
How about this?

274
00:17:18,832 --> 00:17:20,680
Help me withhold Gao Yang's school records.

275
00:17:20,680 --> 00:17:23,219
Calm down. I don't have the right to do that.

276
00:17:23,219 --> 00:17:24,860
What should I do then?

277
00:17:24,860 --> 00:17:28,559
Oh, that's right, the Household Register.

278
00:17:29,359 --> 00:17:31,160
The Household Register is at home.

279
00:17:31,160 --> 00:17:33,039
I'll tear it up when I go home.

280
00:17:33,039 --> 00:17:36,419
Bin, you're a teacher after all.

281
00:17:36,419 --> 00:17:38,179
Can't you communicate nicely when you encounter a problem?

282
00:17:38,179 --> 00:17:39,699
If we can communicate, would we get divorced?

283
00:17:39,699 --> 00:17:41,419
Anna only believes in money.

284
00:17:41,419 --> 00:17:43,359
She'll ruin my son, do you understand?

285
00:17:43,359 --> 00:17:45,219
That's an overstatement.

286
00:17:45,219 --> 00:17:47,819
Anna is his mom after all.

287
00:17:47,819 --> 00:17:50,240
She wants to transfer him to another school for his own good.

288
00:17:50,240 --> 00:17:53,119
Besides, Gao Yang is about to become an adult.

289
00:17:53,119 --> 00:17:57,139
He has the right to choose who he wants to live with.

290
00:17:58,359 --> 00:18:00,200
Whose side are you on?

291
00:18:00,880 --> 00:18:02,760
Did Anna pay you?

292
00:18:02,760 --> 00:18:05,980
You're on the wrong side!

293
00:18:09,300 --> 00:18:11,560
You're so childish!

294
00:18:11,560 --> 00:18:13,160
What is this poem about?
[Class 3, Grade 2]

295
00:18:13,160 --> 00:18:16,600
It's about Li Bai's journey from Shandong to Zhejiang

296
00:18:16,600 --> 00:18:19,659
after he was exiled from Chang'an.

297
00:18:21,451 --> 00:18:23,020
What are you doing?

298
00:18:23,020 --> 00:18:25,179
Where do want to toss that?

299
00:18:27,720 --> 00:18:29,400
Where did I say Li Bai was going?

300
00:18:29,400 --> 00:18:31,039
Li Bai?

301
00:18:31,039 --> 00:18:34,760
Li Bai was... going to Beijing.

302
00:18:34,760 --> 00:18:37,020
You look like Beijing!

303
00:18:37,020 --> 00:18:38,720
Bring that to my office after class.

304
00:18:38,720 --> 00:18:40,551
Roger that.

305
00:18:42,750 --> 00:18:45,350
[Office]

306
00:18:45,359 --> 00:18:47,699
I want you to consider your future carefully.

307
00:18:47,699 --> 00:18:50,160
My future is in Beijing.

308
00:18:50,160 --> 00:18:52,459
You think I don't know you, Gao Yang?

309
00:18:52,459 --> 00:18:54,299
Why must you go to Beijing?

310
00:18:54,299 --> 00:18:56,799
You just have problems with your dad and you want to get away from him.

311
00:18:56,799 --> 00:18:58,600
No, that's not it.

312
00:18:58,600 --> 00:19:02,940
As the ancient saying goes, "Water flows down. Men move up."

313
00:19:02,940 --> 00:19:06,008
What do you mean? Tieyuan is keeping you from moving up?

314
00:19:06,008 --> 00:19:07,739
Isn't our No. 3 High School a nice school?

315
00:19:07,739 --> 00:19:09,699
I'm a famous teacher in Tieyuan too.

316
00:19:09,699 --> 00:19:11,599
I agree.

317
00:19:11,599 --> 00:19:15,620
It's true! Look at my former students, each one of them turned out great. It's true.

318
00:19:15,620 --> 00:19:17,060
Look, Li Qingtong.

319
00:19:17,060 --> 00:19:19,900
She had such bad grades at the time. She still ended up going to college.

320
00:19:19,900 --> 00:19:23,179
Look at Wu Zhixun, he repeated school and went to Beijing University.

321
00:19:23,179 --> 00:19:26,640
These are all living proof! They are all here.

322
00:19:26,640 --> 00:19:28,000
You used to be pretty handsome.

323
00:19:28,000 --> 00:19:30,039
I'm not ugly now.

324
00:19:30,039 --> 00:19:33,599
You... You have to take it to heart, understand?

325
00:19:38,459 --> 00:19:41,490
Wait, something feels wrong.

326
00:19:41,490 --> 00:19:43,000
Did Gao Bin pay you?

327
00:19:43,000 --> 00:19:44,419
You just...

328
00:19:44,419 --> 00:19:46,200
What does this have to do with your dad?

329
00:19:46,200 --> 00:19:49,040
You watched me... I watched you grow up.

330
00:19:49,040 --> 00:19:51,040
I just want to tell you how I really feel.

331
00:19:51,040 --> 00:19:53,019
That's right.

332
00:19:53,019 --> 00:19:54,340
How many years have we known each other?

333
00:19:54,340 --> 00:19:56,979
I know what you want to say as soon as you open your mouth.

334
00:19:56,979 --> 00:19:59,279
Forget about what I want to say.

335
00:19:59,279 --> 00:20:02,079
Listen to your heart and find out what you really want.

336
00:20:02,079 --> 00:20:04,459
Yes, your dad isn't rich.

337
00:20:04,459 --> 00:20:06,019
But he gave you everything.

338
00:20:06,019 --> 00:20:07,759
Think about it, over the past ten years,

339
00:20:07,759 --> 00:20:09,939
who carried you to the hospital when you got sick?

340
00:20:09,939 --> 00:20:14,540
Who apologized for you when you caused trouble? Am I right?

341
00:20:14,540 --> 00:20:18,019
Let me tell you, every teacher in the school wanted to set your dad with someone.

342
00:20:18,019 --> 00:20:21,160
I'm over thirty years old. I've been single for so many years and no one cares.

343
00:20:21,160 --> 00:20:25,660
Let me tell you, no matter how pretty and nice they are, your dad never approved any of them. Why?

344
00:20:25,660 --> 00:20:29,439
Because he's afraid it might hurt you if he gets married again. He's afraid you can't handle it.

345
00:20:29,439 --> 00:20:33,019
He remained single all this time because of his son.

346
00:20:33,019 --> 00:20:36,212
Over the past ten years, was it easy for him to be both parents?

347
00:20:37,000 --> 00:20:38,517
Am I right?

348
00:20:39,319 --> 00:20:40,739
Yes, you're growing up.

349
00:20:40,739 --> 00:20:43,059
Isn't your dad getting older too?

350
00:20:43,059 --> 00:20:44,820
Now, you're going to Beijing.

351
00:20:44,820 --> 00:20:48,070
Are you willing to leave your dad here all by himself?

352
00:20:55,499 --> 00:20:57,409
Mr. Wu.

353
00:20:57,409 --> 00:20:59,900
You have to take it to heart.

354
00:20:59,900 --> 00:21:03,956
Compared to Gao Bin, I'm more reluctant to leave you.

355
00:21:04,000 --> 00:21:05,960
You have to take care of yourself.

356
00:21:05,960 --> 00:21:08,659
I'll leave the CD to you.

357
00:21:11,920 --> 00:21:13,590
You just won't listen.

358
00:21:14,859 --> 00:21:18,482
You're... I'm so pissed off.

359
00:21:26,140 --> 00:21:28,279
Beibei, women shouldn't sigh.

360
00:21:28,279 --> 00:21:30,480
It will make you ten years older.

361
00:21:30,480 --> 00:21:35,120
Meng, what if Gao Yang can't eat popsicles anymore

362
00:21:35,120 --> 00:21:38,200
when he gets to Beijing?

363
00:21:38,200 --> 00:21:39,700
How is that possible?

364
00:21:39,700 --> 00:21:43,100
Beijing is a big city. They have everything there.

365
00:21:44,699 --> 00:21:47,419
Beibei, if you really miss Gao Yang,

366
00:21:47,419 --> 00:21:49,580
just apply for a college in Beijing.

367
00:21:49,580 --> 00:21:52,359
It's too late when I get there.

368
00:21:52,359 --> 00:21:55,200
I don't know how many new friends Gao Yang would have made by then.

369
00:21:55,200 --> 00:21:58,140
That won't happen. New friends aren't as nice as you.

370
00:21:58,140 --> 00:22:00,300
With your condition...

371
00:22:04,179 --> 00:22:06,060
What condition do I have?

372
00:22:06,060 --> 00:22:07,960
Meng, you have good grades.

373
00:22:07,960 --> 00:22:09,599
Jia, you are a long-distance runner.

374
00:22:09,599 --> 00:22:12,060
I have nothing besides a pretty face.

375
00:22:12,060 --> 00:22:14,459
I'm so distressed.

376
00:22:24,140 --> 00:22:29,077
If Gao Yang leaves, there won't be a decent boy in our school anymore.

377
00:22:33,499 --> 00:22:35,019
Hello.

378
00:22:35,019 --> 00:22:36,499
Who is this?

379
00:22:36,499 --> 00:22:39,619
I'm Piao Jiutong, Leader of the Korean Interest Group.

380
00:22:39,619 --> 00:22:42,480
I'm in Mi Jia's class.

381
00:22:43,559 --> 00:22:45,939
Mi Jia, I'm not a bad student.

382
00:22:45,939 --> 00:22:47,880
You don't have to resist me like that.

383
00:22:47,880 --> 00:22:51,300
Well, we need a girl in the Korean Interest Group. Come join us.

384
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:53,859
I... I... No... No, I won't.

385
00:22:53,859 --> 00:22:55,979
Mi Jia, that's your fault.

386
00:22:55,979 --> 00:22:59,780
You'll have an easier time watching Korean dramas if you learn Korean, right?

387
00:22:59,780 --> 00:23:03,680
Let me teach you. Do you know how to say "I like you"?

388
00:23:03,680 --> 00:23:05,079
I love you.

389
00:23:05,920 --> 00:23:08,980
I can't stand it anymore! I'm so disgusted!

390
00:23:08,980 --> 00:23:12,459
I'm talking to Mi Jia about Korean. Shut up.

391
00:23:12,459 --> 00:23:14,259
Oh, God.

392
00:23:14,259 --> 00:23:16,759
Geez, do you want to die?

393
00:23:16,759 --> 00:23:20,860
Are you crazy? Who the hell are you?

394
00:23:20,860 --> 00:23:23,500
- Let's go.
- Let's go.

395
00:23:25,359 --> 00:23:28,680
Bei-Beibei, you can speak Korean?

396
00:23:28,680 --> 00:23:30,699
What Korean? I am of the Chaoxian Nationality.

397
00:23:30,699 --> 00:23:34,340
That's my native dialect. I don't like to speak it normally.

398
00:23:34,340 --> 00:23:36,280
Come on.

399
00:23:38,059 --> 00:23:40,259
Come on, Xiaowen. Take a seat.

400
00:23:44,899 --> 00:23:47,279
Why do you want to see me, Mr. Gao?

401
00:23:49,880 --> 00:23:53,280
Xiaowen, you're a sensible boy.

402
00:23:53,280 --> 00:23:57,340
Can you help me convince Gao Yang?

403
00:23:58,279 --> 00:24:00,160
You boys can communicate better.

404
00:24:00,160 --> 00:24:02,760
He won't listen to me.

405
00:24:02,760 --> 00:24:04,480
But Gao Yang already decided to leave.

406
00:24:04,480 --> 00:24:06,140
His decision doesn't count.

407
00:24:06,140 --> 00:24:07,920
The college entrance exam is around the corner.

408
00:24:07,920 --> 00:24:09,739
What would he do if he goes to Beijing?

409
00:24:09,739 --> 00:24:12,859
Doesn't Beijing have a better education system?

410
00:24:14,799 --> 00:24:15,860
Let me put it this way.

411
00:24:15,860 --> 00:24:19,700
When Gao Yang was 6 years old, his mom and I got divorced.

412
00:24:19,700 --> 00:24:22,620
His mom doesn't care about him at all.

413
00:24:22,620 --> 00:24:25,919
When Gao Yang cried for his mom,

414
00:24:25,919 --> 00:24:29,699
she didn't even have time to answer the phone.

415
00:24:30,620 --> 00:24:33,979
Now, she wants to take Gao Yang to Beijing.

416
00:24:33,979 --> 00:24:35,900
Does she have time now?

417
00:24:35,900 --> 00:24:37,739
Can she take good care of Gao Yang now?

418
00:24:37,739 --> 00:24:41,760
Gao Yang said, his mom didn't have time.

419
00:24:41,760 --> 00:24:43,862
But she can hire a private tutor.

420
00:24:46,499 --> 00:24:52,100
But... a private tutor is just working for money.

421
00:24:52,100 --> 00:24:55,639
They would be off duty when it's time. Can they replace parents?

422
00:24:55,639 --> 00:24:58,440
Gao Yang shouldn't go to Beijing.

423
00:24:59,359 --> 00:25:05,290
Xiaowen, please help me convince him.

424
00:25:06,019 --> 00:25:11,540
But I still think Gao Yang should make his own choices in life.

425
00:25:27,939 --> 00:25:31,639
Tieyuan is so boring even if I look at it upside down.

426
00:25:31,639 --> 00:25:35,179
♪ If you love me, don't leave ♪

427
00:25:35,179 --> 00:25:38,419
♪ Unless you said ♪

428
00:25:38,419 --> 00:25:42,740
♪ you don't love me ♪

429
00:25:43,680 --> 00:25:45,520
Well done, Bro.

430
00:25:45,520 --> 00:25:47,799
But it doesn't matter how sad the song is,

431
00:25:47,799 --> 00:25:49,819
I have to go.

432
00:25:49,819 --> 00:25:53,320
You're overthinking. I'm not sad because of you. It's just a sad song.

433
00:25:53,320 --> 00:25:56,019
What do you mean? You're not sad to see me go?

434
00:25:56,019 --> 00:25:58,220
I am. I'm really sad.

435
00:25:58,220 --> 00:26:00,039
I... I'm really sad.

436
00:26:03,119 --> 00:26:07,179
Actually, I feel really bad when I see how much you guys want me to stay.

437
00:26:07,179 --> 00:26:08,720
Beibei cried so hard.

438
00:26:08,720 --> 00:26:11,739
Mr. Wu Dibao also said nice things to me.

439
00:26:13,039 --> 00:26:16,660
Actually, I do want to stay for a few more days.

440
00:26:26,839 --> 00:26:28,200
Good.

441
00:26:28,200 --> 00:26:31,200
You ended it on a positive note.

442
00:26:31,200 --> 00:26:34,780
However, on the bright side, you get to see Wang Cailing

443
00:26:34,780 --> 00:26:38,300
and you won't be beaten up by Dong Dawei if you go to Beijing.

444
00:26:38,300 --> 00:26:39,982
That's nice.

445
00:26:43,379 --> 00:26:45,940
I forgot about Dong Dawei.

446
00:26:45,940 --> 00:26:48,060
Why? You want to say goodbye to him too?

447
00:26:48,060 --> 00:26:51,179
Of course. Always finish what you start.

448
00:26:57,499 --> 00:27:00,260
You're asking for it.

449
00:27:15,060 --> 00:27:20,459
Dawei, I'll leave No. 3 High School's goal to you now.

450
00:27:22,820 --> 00:27:24,680
Don't worry, Mr. Gao.

451
00:27:24,680 --> 00:27:26,880
Watch your center of gravity.

452
00:27:29,499 --> 00:27:31,372
Your center of gravity.

453
00:27:35,499 --> 00:27:37,599
- Dawei.
- Mr. Gao.

454
00:27:38,499 --> 00:27:41,079
How do you feel? Can you keep up?

455
00:27:41,079 --> 00:27:43,820
Don't just focus on your training. Your studies are important too.

456
00:27:43,820 --> 00:27:45,389
Got it.

457
00:27:47,279 --> 00:27:50,839
If you need anything, come to me at anytime.

458
00:27:53,380 --> 00:27:55,920
Our school's soccer team is terrible. We lost at 5:0.

459
00:27:55,920 --> 00:27:59,820
Exactly, that goalie is useless. He's rubbish.

460
00:28:03,019 --> 00:28:05,040
It's fine if we lose a game.

461
00:28:05,040 --> 00:28:08,419
Don't listen to them. We'll win it back next time.

462
00:28:10,620 --> 00:28:13,079
Keep your chin up, all of you. Don't be dispirited.

463
00:28:13,079 --> 00:28:16,780
Why didn't Mr. Gao come to such an important game?

464
00:28:16,780 --> 00:28:19,459
He said he'd take us to the championship too. Bullshit!

465
00:28:19,459 --> 00:28:21,240
Mr. Gao took the day off.

466
00:28:21,240 --> 00:28:24,120
It's our fault for losing the game. Don't blame the coach.

467
00:28:24,920 --> 00:28:27,699
He comes late and leaves early all the time. Has he ever explained to us?

468
00:28:27,699 --> 00:28:29,519
Exactly. He's so busy.

469
00:28:29,519 --> 00:28:31,640
He doesn't take the team seriously at all.

470
00:28:31,640 --> 00:28:33,219
All the teachers in the school look down upon him.

471
00:28:33,219 --> 00:28:36,160
Gao Bin is useless!

472
00:28:37,659 --> 00:28:39,000
Watch your mouth.

473
00:28:39,000 --> 00:28:40,419
So what if I'm dissing him?

474
00:28:40,419 --> 00:28:43,019
You listened to him and you still let them get five goals.

475
00:28:43,019 --> 00:28:44,699
You call yourself the goalkeeper of No. 3 High School.

476
00:28:44,699 --> 00:28:47,279
- You're a colander!
- Say that again!

477
00:28:47,279 --> 00:28:50,859
I said, he's useless and you're a colander!

478
00:28:50,859 --> 00:28:53,736
Say that again! Say that again!

479
00:28:53,759 --> 00:28:56,320
- Stop fighting!
- Be careful!

480
00:28:58,870 --> 00:29:00,750
Say it again!

481
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:07,928
Who started it?

482
00:29:07,928 --> 00:29:11,153
- Mr. Gao, I...
- I asked you who started it?

483
00:29:14,140 --> 00:29:15,927
I started it.

484
00:29:20,179 --> 00:29:22,335
Hand me your gloves.

485
00:29:25,459 --> 00:29:27,138
Hand them over.

486
00:29:34,340 --> 00:29:36,157
Hand them over.

487
00:29:43,459 --> 00:29:45,580
Dawei, I told you,

488
00:29:46,419 --> 00:29:50,239
the results were not important. But you can't fight.

489
00:29:50,239 --> 00:29:53,282
The team rules stated anyone who fights...

490
00:29:54,100 --> 00:29:56,119
will be dismissed.

491
00:30:23,860 --> 00:30:28,459
Brother Dong, are you overlooking your territory?

492
00:30:29,900 --> 00:30:32,500
Are you insane?

493
00:30:32,500 --> 00:30:34,399
Don't yell at me.

494
00:30:34,399 --> 00:30:40,400
Well, our feud has been going on for almost a year, right?

495
00:30:41,000 --> 00:30:43,419
It's time to put an end to it.

496
00:30:44,739 --> 00:30:47,600
- What do you want to do?
- A solo match.

497
00:30:49,799 --> 00:30:52,620
Wait, what does that sneer mean?

498
00:30:52,620 --> 00:30:54,400
You really think I can't beat you?

499
00:30:54,400 --> 00:30:57,199
Normally, either you or I have more people around us.

500
00:30:57,199 --> 00:31:02,279
Today, do you dare to do a solo match with me?

501
00:31:02,279 --> 00:31:03,860
Let's do it after school tomorrow.

502
00:31:03,860 --> 00:31:07,420
No, let's do it now. Come on.

503
00:31:08,659 --> 00:31:11,019
Your don't get to decide when to have a solo match.

504
00:31:11,019 --> 00:31:14,016
You won't have a chance when I go to Beijing.

505
00:31:15,559 --> 00:31:19,050
Niu Wanwan already likes someone else. Did you know?

506
00:31:20,599 --> 00:31:22,469
What are you talking about?

507
00:31:23,419 --> 00:31:26,459
Do you want to know who it is?

508
00:31:29,340 --> 00:31:31,299
About Niu Wanwan,

509
00:31:31,299 --> 00:31:35,900
you should know who she likes, right?

510
00:31:35,900 --> 00:31:42,219
She likes a man who's strong and powerful.

511
00:31:43,259 --> 00:31:46,540
The one she likes is... me!

512
00:31:46,540 --> 00:31:48,364
Gao Yang,

513
00:31:49,259 --> 00:31:50,954
stop right there!

514
00:31:53,939 --> 00:31:56,292
- Gao Yang!
- Come and get me!

515
00:32:01,799 --> 00:32:04,319
Come on, keep running.

516
00:32:04,319 --> 00:32:06,140
Dawei, wait.

517
00:32:06,140 --> 00:32:08,359
My pants are falling down.

518
00:32:08,359 --> 00:32:10,334
Let me tie it up.

519
00:32:12,660 --> 00:32:14,760
You are such a good runner!

520
00:32:14,760 --> 00:32:16,940
- One to zero.
- Gao Yang!

521
00:32:20,380 --> 00:32:21,934
Gao Yang!

522
00:32:24,319 --> 00:32:26,620
Should we go help Gao Yang?

523
00:32:26,620 --> 00:32:29,399
No. He must've caused the trouble.

524
00:32:29,399 --> 00:32:32,000
- What are you doing, Zhao Jiabao?
- Let me have some!

525
00:32:32,000 --> 00:32:35,540
My dad only gave me so much allowance this month! Let me have some!

526
00:32:35,540 --> 00:32:36,599
- I just want a bite!
- What are you doing?

527
00:32:36,599 --> 00:32:38,280
- I just want a bite!
- Meng, stop him!

528
00:32:38,280 --> 00:32:41,300
What are you doing? You're a man. Why are you
fighting a girl for snacks?

529
00:32:41,300 --> 00:32:42,419
Who knows?

530
00:32:42,419 --> 00:32:44,699
Didn't I tell you? Why are you fighting with him?

531
00:32:44,699 --> 00:32:46,459
Look at those students who are studying behind you!

532
00:32:46,459 --> 00:32:50,259
Look at you! Who else is making a scene on campus like the two of you?

533
00:32:50,259 --> 00:32:53,100
- Gao Yang stop right there!
- Help!

534
00:32:53,100 --> 00:32:54,979
What's going on? Stop it!

535
00:32:54,979 --> 00:32:56,380
No one is allowed to hit Gao Yang!

536
00:32:56,380 --> 00:32:58,680
- Gao Yang, I'm here!
- Beibei, slow down!

537
00:32:58,680 --> 00:33:00,380
Help!

538
00:33:00,380 --> 00:33:02,107
Don't fight!

539
00:33:05,880 --> 00:33:06,919
- Stop!
- Gao Yang!

540
00:33:06,919 --> 00:33:10,680
Don't fight! Let go! No fighting in school!

541
00:33:10,680 --> 00:33:12,319
Stop fighting!

542
00:33:12,319 --> 00:33:13,640
Get up!

543
00:33:13,640 --> 00:33:16,420
Let go of me!

544
00:33:18,020 --> 00:33:19,880
- What are you doing?
- Dong Dawei!

545
00:33:19,880 --> 00:33:21,119
Let go! Let go!

546
00:33:21,119 --> 00:33:23,120
Stop looking!

547
00:33:23,120 --> 00:33:25,660
Stop, stop fighting! Stop fighting!

548
00:33:25,660 --> 00:33:27,760
I'm the principal! Listen to me! Do you hear me?

549
00:33:27,760 --> 00:33:30,079
Let go! Let go!

550
00:33:33,440 --> 00:33:35,519
Who pushed me?

551
00:33:43,640 --> 00:33:45,533
Who did that?

552
00:33:45,533 --> 00:33:47,780
Who pushed me?

553
00:34:18,160 --> 00:34:24,211
♫  I know the direction of dawn  ♫

554
00:34:24,211 --> 00:34:31,476
♫  It's right in front of me, waiting for me to shine  ♫

555
00:34:31,476 --> 00:34:37,566
♫  The starlight that shines alone the way  ♫

556
00:34:37,566 --> 00:34:43,606
♫  Accompanying me on my adventure, packing my dreams in my heart  ♫

557
00:34:43,606 --> 00:34:50,158
♫  I don't fear the rough journey ahead, I will no longer run away  ♫

558
00:34:50,158 --> 00:34:55,898
♫  Maybe I'm not destined for the hardship of this journey  ♫

559
00:34:55,898 --> 00:34:59,785
♫  And chase after the longing in my heart  ♫

560
00:34:59,785 --> 00:35:03,133
♫  Let set sail on your dreams  ♫

561
00:35:03,133 --> 00:35:06,528
♫  Let's not have any regrets in our youth  ♫

562
00:35:06,528 --> 00:35:13,188
♫  Even if you stumble and fall, you'll have me by your side  ♫

563
00:35:13,188 --> 00:35:16,499
♫  Let's find the answer through the madness  ♫

564
00:35:16,499 --> 00:35:20,611
♫  Let's have courage to ride the waves and billows  ♫

565
00:35:20,611 --> 00:35:24,431
♫  With my wings, I'll fly us to the future  ♫

566
00:35:24,431 --> 00:35:32,391
♫  And step forward into the future without fear of sorrow  ♫
